    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re locked in a global race against a shadowy force to uncover esoteric secrets buried beneath World War II and the Cold War. From forgotten bunkers and abandoned research facilities to black-site laboratories erased from history, every firefight brings you closer to forbidden technologies capable of reshaping reality itself. Unearth classified weapons, you race a rival faction across the globe, decoding symbols, discovering prototypes, and unleashing experimental weapons that bend space, time, and perception. Every secret you unlock pushes the world closer to a second, unseen arms race—one where the deadliest weapon is knowledge itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/cb5762c173b3c7e6933560161b312205.poster.avif?t=1771816970\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/cb5762c173b3c7e6933560161b312205.webm?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/cb5762c173b3c7e6933560161b312205.mp4?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features seven fully functioning game modes</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rush</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Confirmed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team Deathmatch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture the Flag</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search and Destroy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free for All</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/f59ef98eb1414fdcbfb7157d12a181a8.poster.avif?t=1771816970\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/f59ef98eb1414fdcbfb7157d12a181a8.webm?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/f59ef98eb1414fdcbfb7157d12a181a8.mp4?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Red Crucible Assault currently has three unique arenas with dynamic weather ranging from sunny, night and storm conditions. More arenas are in development and will be released soon.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vault Prizrak</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Air Strip (Day, night and storm)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Island-X (Day - conquest game mode only for testing)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operation Highjump2</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base-211 (conquest game mode only for testing)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/3e20ea4ae082f0d14922f99329f999ff.poster.avif?t=1771816970\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/3e20ea4ae082f0d14922f99329f999ff.webm?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/3e20ea4ae082f0d14922f99329f999ff.mp4?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can customize their loadouts with a wide array of weapons, including assault rifles, sniper rifles, submachine guns, melee weapons and exotic historic and prototype firearms. Each weapon can be modified with attachments to suit individual preferences. New weapons are continually being added to the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The progression system we are working on will allow players to unlock new weapon skins as they gain experience and complete challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/4c7219501503c21039c78f8410617c41.poster.avif?t=1771816970\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/4c7219501503c21039c78f8410617c41.webm?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/4c7219501503c21039c78f8410617c41.mp4?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With smooth gunplay mechanics, responsive controls, and a high-skill ceiling, the game offers both casual and competitive players an adrenaline-pumping shooter experience that rewards strategy, teamwork, and individual skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/a4a99a47923a890d007e383b6a69d2b6.poster.avif?t=1771816970\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/a4a99a47923a890d007e383b6a69d2b6.webm?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325950/extras/a4a99a47923a890d007e383b6a69d2b6.mp4?t=1771816970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
